## Navigation Structure

```
RootNavigator
├── AuthNavigator (Stack) — shown when user = null
│   ├── Login
│   ├── Register
│   ├── ForgotPassword
│   └── ResetPassword
└── AppNavigator (Stack) — shown when user exists
    ├── Tabs (BottomTab) — order matches web app
    │   ├── Dashboard
    │   ├── Plans
    │   ├── Progress
    │   ├── Catalog        ← Exercise Catalog (5th tab, matches web)
    │   └── Profile
    ├── Onboarding (fullScreenModal)
    ├── WorkoutSession (fullScreenModal)
    ├── WorkoutSessionExerciseDetail (modal)
    ├── GenerateWorkout (fullScreenModal)
    ├── WorkoutPreview
    ├── ExercisePicker (modal)
    ├── ExerciseDetail
    ├── CreatePlan / EditPlan
    ├── CreateWorkout / EditWorkout
    ├── ManageExercises
    ├── ProgramLibrary / ProgramDetail
    ├── RoutineDetail / RoutineWorkoutDetail
    └── SessionDetail
```

